            </svg>
          </div>
          <span class="font-display font-bold text-xl">
            <span class="text-primary-400">Bird</span><span class="text-secondary-400">kanfly</span>
          </span>
        </a>
        <p class="text-slate-400 mb-6">
          Premier flight training academy in Mysore. Your journey to the skies begins here.
